title: WHAT U WANT BE ?
author: Vaibhav Khushalani
readmore: Avinash Chauhan along with his partner Akshit Singh Soni own BooksOnGo an online bookstore. The two best friends came up with a platform to provide books at economical prices and create a community for book lovers.
blog:
Tell us something about your business ?

- Akshit: “We own an online start-up named Booksongo, here we provide all kind of reading material on Instagram and it’s a 100% Indian brand. We have a huge and varied collection of reading material from which our customers can choose from.”
